===Pronunciation===
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|en|/ˌkæt.əˈkɹiː.sɪs/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|catachreses}}

# A [[misuse]] of a [[word]]; an [[application]] of a [[term]] to something which it does not properly [[denote]].<ref name="OED"/>
## {{lb|en|often, especially}} Such a misuse involving some similarity of sound between the misused word and the appropriate word.
# {{lb|en|rhetoric}} A [[misapplication]] or [[overextension]] of [[figurative]] or [[analogical]] [[description]]; a [[wrongly]] [[applied]] [[metaphor]] or [[trope]].<ref name="OED"/>
#* {{RQ:Langley Rhetoric|14|A '''''Catachresis''''' terms abused receives,<br/>And epithets and attributes improper gives.}}

